fm: int largestSubmatrix(vector<vector<int>>& matrix) {         int m = matrix.size(), n = matrix[0].size();         vector<int> h(n, 0);         int res = 0;         for (int i = 0; i < m; i++) {             multiset<int> s;             for (int j = 0; j < n; j++) {                 if (matrix[i][j] == 0)                     h[j] = 0;                 else                     h[j] += 1;                 s.insert(h[j]);             }             int cnt = 1, ans = 0;             for (auto it = s.rbegin(); it != s.rend() && *it != 0; it++, cnt++) {                 ans = max(ans, cnt * (*it));             }             res = max(res, ans);         }         return res;     }
